However, he said he had been encouraged by the global reaction to "my act of political expression."
Citizens around the world as well as senior officials – including in the United States – have judged the revelation of an inexplicable system of permanent surveillance to be of public utility.
The letter calls for an offer of cooperation with the German authorities “when the difficulties of this humanitarian situation have been resolved”.
